-
-- Alter resource using standard mode
-
-```sql
-ALTER RESOURCE ds_0 (
-    HOST=127.0.0.1,
-    PORT=3306,
-    DB=db_0,
-    USER=root,
-    PASSWORD=root
-);
-```
-
